text: Russell Eric Wilson Mawhinney (born 28 March 1960 in Ranfurly) was a New Zealand cricketer who played for Northern Districts, Griqualand West and Otago in first-class cricket. He is currently married to TVNZ presenter Matty McLean. ==Other websites== * Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Bisexual people Category:New Zealand LGBT people Category:LGBT sportspeople
